<inglise>Implementing Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;kaitseseaduse alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktide kehtivus </eesti>
<inglise>Validity of legislation issued on basis of Republic of Estonia Labour Protection Act </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;kaitseseaduse (RT I 1992, 25, 343; RT I 1996, 49, 953) alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktid kehtivad p&auml;rast k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist niiv&otilde;rd, kuiv&otilde;rd need ei ole vastuolus k&auml;esoleva seadusega, ja seni, kuni need kas t&uuml;histatakse v&otilde;i viiakse k&auml;esoleva seadusega vastavusse. </eesti>
<inglise>The legislation issued on the basis of the Republic of Estonia Labour Protection Act (RT I 1992, 25, 343; RT I 1996, 49, 953) is valid after the entry into force of this Act in so far as it is not contrary to this Act and until it is repealed or brought into compliance with this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu seaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Republic of Estonia Employment Contracts Act </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;lepingu seaduse (RT 1992, 15/16, 241; 1993, 10, 150; RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 14, 170; 16, 228; 1996, 3, 57; 40, 773; 45, 850; 49, 953; 1997, 5/6, 32; 1998, 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 276; 60, 616; 2000, 25, 144) &sect; 48 l&otilde;ike 1 punkt 2 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>Clause 48 (1) 2) of the Republic of Estonia Employment Contracts Act (RT 1992, 15/16, 241; 1993, 10, 150; RT I 1993, 26, 441; 1995, 14, 170; 16, 228; 1996, 3, 57; 40, 773; 45, 850; 49, 953; 1997, 5/6, 32; 1998, 111, 1829; 1999, 16, 276; 60, 616; 2000, 25, 144) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"2) t&auml;itma t&ouml;&ouml;sisekorra, t&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu, t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse ning tuleohutuse n&otilde;udeid;". </eesti>
<inglise>"2) comply with the requirements of internal work procedure rules and with the occupational health and safety and fire safety requirements;" </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. </inglise>
<eesti>Kriminaalkoodeksi muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Criminal Code </inglise>
<eesti>Kriminaalkoodeksi (RT 1992, 20, 287 ja 288; RT I 1999, 38, 485; 57, 595, 597; 60, 616; 57, 598; 97, 859; 102, 907; 2000, 10, 55; 28, 167; 29, 173; 33, 193; 40, 247; 49, 301, 305) &sect; 135 pealkiri ja l&otilde;ige 1 muudetakse ning s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>The title of &sect; 135 and subsection 135 (1) of the Criminal Code (RT 1992, 20, 287 and 288; RT I 1999, 38, 485; 57, 595, 597; 60, 616; 57, 598; 97, 859; 102, 907; 2000, 10, 55; 28, 167; 29, 173; 33, 193; 40, 247; 49, 301, 305) are amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 135. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 135. </inglise>
<eesti>T&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse n&otilde;uete rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Violation of occupational health and safety requirements </inglise>
<eesti>(1) T&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest nende t&auml;itmise eest vastutava isiku poolt, kui see rikkumine v&otilde;is kaasa tuua &otilde;nnetusjuhtumi inimesega v&otilde;i muu raske tagaj&auml;rje, - karistatakse rahatrahviga." </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A violation of occupational health and safety requirements by a person responsible for compliance therewith if the violation may have resulted in an accident involving a person or brought about any other serious consequence is punishable by a fine." </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendments to Code of Administrative Offences </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, &otilde;iend; 58, 608; 95, 843; 2000, 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301 ja 305) &sect; 34 l&otilde;ige 1 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>Subsection 34 (1) of the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, Correction Notice) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(1) T&ouml;&ouml;&otilde;iguse aktide n&otilde;uete, sealhulgas t&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest nende t&auml;itmise eest vastutava isiku poolt - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni saja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses." </eesti>
<inglise>"(1) A fine of up to one hundred days' wages shall be imposed for a violation of requirements of employment legislation, including occupational health and safety requirements, by a person responsible for compliance therewith." </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>Kollektiivlepingu seaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Collective Agreements Act </inglise>
<eesti>Kollektiivlepingu seaduse (RT I 1993, 20, 353; 1999, 60, 616; 57, 372) &sect;-s 6 tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 6 of the Collective Agreements Act (RT I 1993, 20, 353) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) l&otilde;ike 1 punkt 6 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>1) clause (1) 6) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"6) t&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse tingimused;"; </eesti>
<inglise>"6) occupational health and safety conditions;"; </inglise>
<eesti>2) l&otilde;ike 2 punkt 2 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>2) clause (2) 2) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"2) t&ouml;&ouml;tervishoiu ja t&ouml;&ouml;ohutuse tagamiseks rakendatavad lisaabin&otilde;ud;". </eesti>
<inglise>"2) additional measures to be implemented to ensure occupational health and safety;". </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;igusaktide kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Repeal of legislation </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel tunnistatakse kehtetuks Eesti Vabariigi t&ouml;&ouml;kaitseseadus (RT 1992, 25, 343; RT I 1996, 49, 953) ja Eesti NSV t&ouml;&ouml;koodeksi (ENSV Teataja 1972, 28, lisa 1; 1984, 16, 178; 49, 577; 1988, 30, 376) &sect;-d 147-162. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon the entry into force of this Act, the Republic of Estonia Labour Protection Act (RT 1992, 25, 343; RT I 1996, 49, 953) and &sect;&sect; 147-162 of the Estonian SSR Labour Code (ENSV Teataja (3) 1972, 28, Appendix 1; 1984, 16, 178; 49, 577; 1988, 30, 376) are repealed. (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>


